com.hunterjdev.mockjdbc

  • Classes in com.hunterjdev.mockjdbc used by com.hunterjdev.mockjdbc 
    Class and Description
    MockDriver.MockObjectHandler
    MockObjectHandler is the primary controller and invocation handler for proxy objects.
    ResultSetProvider
    ResultSetProvider is used to encapsulate the logic needed to provide mock ResultSet objects to MockDriver in cases where multiple ResultSet objects are needed by the code under test.
    TestAction
    TestAction is the base class to extend in order to implement the test code which will be run within the MockDriver context.
